as blue sky clients use app

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:47.450
password authentication.

00:07:47.450 --> 00:07:48.080
So yeah, there are a bunch of really cool mc

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:48.080
p servers out there and you can use them to attach to

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:48.080
your agents and reduce hallucinations.

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:56.700
And ground your development in the official

